{
  "id": "637a58c1439501001df0e3eb",
  "title": "ファイル名をランダムに生成するスクリプト",
  "created": 1668962498,
  "updated": 1776679135,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "637a58c1439501001df0e3eb",
      "text": "ファイル名をランダムに生成するスクリプト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073743b",
      "text": "from [青空文庫のルビを取るテキスト処理を習得してみよう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c7aff09e0000737461",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962503,
      "updated": 1668962503
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073743c",
      "text": "プログラマーの最初の関門[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962503
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073743e",
      "text": "\t『[ファイル名考えるのだるい]』",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073743f",
      "text": " $ `${Math.round(Math.random()*0xffffffff).toString(16).padStart(8,\"0\")}.arb`",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737440",
      "text": "  でどうや[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737441",
      "text": "  [%  (Math.round(Math.random()*0xffffffff).toString(16).padStart(8,\"0\"))+\".arb\"]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737442",
      "text": "  インラインコード記法は`\\``をエスケープしないといけないのが難点",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737443",
      "text": "  どうにかして[ScrapCalc]で実行できないかなとかって思ってた[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737444",
      "text": "  \tでけた[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737445",
      "text": "  \tよかた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737446",
      "text": "  [ScrapJupyter]なら簡単[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737447",
      "text": "   code:js",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737448",
      "text": "    alert(`${Math.round(Math.random()*0xffffffff).toString(16).padStart(8,\"0\")}.arb`);",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737449",
      "text": "   また知らないUserScriptの名前が…[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744a",
      "text": "   これはひどいwww[wogikaze.icon]",
      "userId": "616ca537c25a92001e5f1e0d",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744b",
      "text": "   生成例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744c",
      "text": "    feb31ac7.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744d",
      "text": "    87aa7f71.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744e",
      "text": "    1776391b.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073744f",
      "text": "  ましなやつにしよう[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737450",
      "text": "   code:2.js",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737451",
      "text": "    const list =scrapbox.Project.pages.filter((page) => /^[a-zA-Z0-9_ ]+$/.test(page.title)).map((page) => page.title.replaceAll(\" \", \"_\"));",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737452",
      "text": "    const head = list[Math.floor(Math.random()*list.length)]??\"dummy\";",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737453",
      "text": "    const tail = list[Math.floor(Math.random()*list.length)]??\"dummy\";",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737454",
      "text": "    await navigator.clipboard.writeText(`${head}-${tail}.arb`);",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737455",
      "text": "   生成例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737456",
      "text": "    JIS-EG.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737457",
      "text": "    scrapebox-Great_Old_One.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737458",
      "text": "    Upnext-PWA.arb",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737459",
      "text": " 酷いw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745a",
      "text": " 理解できない[エンジニアジョーク][cFQ2f7LRuLYP.icon]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745b",
      "text": " 　乱数をなんかやってるらしいのはかろうじて…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745c",
      "text": " 　　解決すると「ファイル名をどうしたらいいかわからない」って言ってる人にファイル名をランダムに生成するスクリプトを渡すジョーク[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745d",
      "text": " 　欧米のジョークを見るときってこんな気分なのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745e",
      "text": "  周りだけ笑って自分だけわからないのつらいのわかる[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e000073745f",
      "text": "  実行しなくてもわかるよう、生成例を貼っておきました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "637a58c1aff09e0000737460",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1668962498,
      "updated": 1668962498
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f7790000000000b67964",
      "text": "[JavaScript.icon]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776678778,
      "updated": 1776678807
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f77c0000000000b67965",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776678780,
      "updated": 1776678780
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f8810000000000b9d76f",
      "text": "[残骸ID]として使ってる[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776679042,
      "updated": 1776679057
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f8980000000000b9d772",
      "text": "\tたとえばOpenAI APIに投げた結果をファイルに書いてエディタで開きたい場合に temp ディレクトリにランダム名でつくらせたりする",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776679065,
      "updated": 1776679101
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f8c30000000000b9d773",
      "text": "\tPKMのような場所であっても、要約や結論以外の「過程に関する記述」を一式隔離したい場合に使える",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776679107,
      "updated": 1776679130
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f8da0000000000b9d774",
      "text": "\t\t残骸IDの意図はこっち",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1776679130,
      "updated": 1776679135
    },
    {
      "id": "69e5f88e0000000000b9d771",
